          <title>Boys Rugby: Cathedral Catholic 28, La Costa Canyon 17</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The High School Boys Rugby Championship was held in Del Mar as the Cathedral Catholic Dons hosted the La Costa Canyon Mavericks. 

